r state pension but may pay tax in the country they live in.  But if you live in <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/si/double.htm\" title=\"Countries with a 'double taxation agreement with the UK’\">a country without a &lsquo;double taxation agreement’</a> you&rsquo;ll have to pay UK tax and may be taxed in the country you live in as well.</p>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>Contact the <a href=\"http://search2.hmrc.gov.uk/kbroker/hmrc/contactus/search.ladv?raction=view&amp;fl0=__dsid%3A&amp;sm=0&amp;ha=34&amp;as=1&amp;sf=&amp;sp_scope=hmrc&amp;sc=hmrc&amp;nh=10&amp;sr=0&amp;cs=ISO-8859-1&amp;tx1=&amp;tx0=49672\" title=\"HMRC Residency Helpline contact details\" rel=\"external\">HM Revenue &amp; Customs (<abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr>) Residency Helpline</a> to find out if you’re classed as a UK resident or not.</p>\n</div>\n\n"}]},"tags":[{"title":"State Pension","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/working%2Fstate-pension.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes calculating State Pension, eligibility, claiming and deferring","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=working%2Fstate-pension","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/working/state-pension"},"parent":{"title":"Working, jobs and pensions","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/working.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes holidays and finding a job","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=working","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/working"},"parent":null}},{"title":"Passports and travelling abroad","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/driving%2Fpassports-travelling-abroad.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes driving abroad, getting a passport, pet passports and bringing goods into the UK","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.g