>\n<p>You may want to pay voluntary contributions because:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>you&rsquo;re close to State Pension age and don&rsquo;t have 30 years of contributions </li>\n  <li>you have gaps in your National Insurance record and want to fill them </li>\n  <li>you know you won&rsquo;t be able to pay 30 years of contributions during your working life and want to avoid gaps (more years for bereavement benefits)</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>However, you have to be <a href=\"/voluntary-national-insurance-contributions/who-can-pay-voluntary-contributions\" title=\"who can pay voluntary contributions\">eligible to pay voluntary contributions.</a></p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"HM Revenue &amp; Customs\">HMRC</abbr> has more information on <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/ni/volcontr/toppingup.htm\" title=\"Deciding if you want to pay voluntary contributions\">deciding if you want to pay voluntary contributions.</a></p>\n\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/voluntary-national-insurance-contributions/who-can-pay-voluntary-contributions","slug":"who-can-pay-voluntary-contributions","order":2,"title":"Who can pay voluntary contributions","body":"<p>The table explains who is eligible to pay voluntary National Insurance contributions and which class to pay.</p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Group</th>\n      <th>Eligible to pay voluntary contributions</th>\n      <th>Current rates</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Employed but earning under £107 a week and not eligible for <a href=\"/boost-state-pension\" title=\"national insurance credits\">National Insurance credits</a></td>\n      <td>Yes</td>\n      <td>Class 3: £13.25 a week</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Self employed with profits under £5,595 and a ‘Small Earnings Certificate’</td>\n      <td>Yes</td>\n      <td>Class 2: £2.65 a week or Class 3: £13.25 a week</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/ni/volcontr/abroad.htm\" title=\"p